            <section>
               <id root="2af8f0bf-cef5-4971-a788-194b5eeb32cc"/>
               <code code="34089-3" codeSystem="2.16.840.1.113883.6.1" displayName="DESCRIPTION SECTION"/>
               <title>Description</title>
               <text>
                  <paragraph>Renal Caps are opaque black oval softgels imprinted "C 162".  These softgels provide water-soluble vitamins.  Renal Caps contain the following inactive ingredients: Blue 1 Lake, gelatin, glycerin, lecithin, Red 40 Lake, soybean oil, starch, titanium dioxide, Yellow # 6 Lake, yellow beeswax.</paragraph>
                  <paragraph>
                     <content styleCode="bold">Each softgel contains:</content>
                  </paragraph>
                  <paragraph>Vitamin C (ascorbic acid)........................100 mg</paragraph>
                  <paragraph>Thiamine (as thiamine mononitrate)..........1.5 mg</paragraph>
                  <paragraph>Riboflavin...............................................1.7 mg</paragraph>
                  <paragraph>Niacin (as niacinamide).............................20 mg</paragraph>
                  <paragraph>Vitamin B<sub>6</sub> (as pyridoxine HCl)...................10 mg</paragraph>
                  <paragraph>Folate (folic acid).........................................1mg</paragraph>
                  <paragraph>Vitamin B<sub>12</sub> (as cyanocobalamin)...............6 mcg</paragraph>
                  <paragraph>Biotin....................................................150 mcg</paragraph>
                  <paragraph>Pantothenic Acid (as calcium pantothenate)..5 mg<br/>
                  </paragraph>
                  <paragraph>
                     <br/>
                  </paragraph>
                  <paragraph/>
               </text>
               <effectiveTime value="20180104"/>
            </section>
         </component>
         <component>
            <section>
               <id root="54f916de-8370-4f23-b908-3ebf1bf2cbe1"/>
               <code code="34067-9" codeSystem="2.16.840.1.113883.6.1" displayName="INDICATIONS &amp; USAGE SECTION"/>
               <title>Indications and Usage</title>
               <text>
                  <paragraph>Renal Caps is indicated in the wasting syndrome of chronic renal failure; uremia and impaired metabolic functions of the kidney.  Renal Caps ia also highly effective as a stress vitamin.<br/>
                  </paragraph>
               </text>
               <effectiveTime value="20180104"/>
            </section>
         </component>
         <component>
            <section>
               <id root="c95c02f8-ad21-48d1-a60d-1e0f28ce6114"/>
               <code code="42232-9" codeSystem="2.16.840.1.113883.6.1" displayName="PRECAUTIONS SECTION"/>
               <title>Precautions</title>
               <text>
                  <paragraph>Folic acid may mask the symptoms of pernicious anemia in that hematologic remission may occur while neurological manifestations progress.<br/>
                  </paragraph>
               </text>
               <effectiveTime value="20180104"/>
            </section>
         </component>
         <component>
            <section>
               <id root="f53392bd-8008-4e74-86a3-148bf01e5133"/>
               <code code="34068-7" codeSystem="2.16.840.1.113883.6.1" displayName="DOSAGE &amp; ADMINISTRATION SECTION"/>
               <title>Dosage and Administration</title>
               <text>
                  <paragraph>One softgel daily, or as directed by physician.  If on dialysis, take after treatment.<br/>
                  </paragraph>
               </text>
               <effectiveTime value="20180104"/>
            </section>
         </component>
