               <code code="44425-7" codeSystem="2.16.840.1.113883.6.1" displayName="STORAGE AND HANDLING SECTION"/>
               <title>Storage</title>
               <text>
                  <br/>
                  <paragraph>Store at controlled room temperature 15-30<sup>o</sup> C (59-86<sup>o</sup>F).  Keep container tightly closed and protected from heat and moisture.</paragraph>
                  <paragraph>
                     <content styleCode="bold">KEEP THIS AND ALL DRUGS OUT OF REACH OF CHILDREN.</content>
                  </paragraph>
